      "description": "Attention enthusiasts and DIY mechanics! This car is ready for a complete transformation and offers a fantastic foundation for your next major project. While it currently requires substantial mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back on the road, it\u2019s a rare chance to own a classic model at a budget-friendly price. Bring your trailer and your vision to give this vehicle a second lease on life!",
